				<p><a href="/cpanel-server-management"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1565" alt="cPanel Server Management Services" src="/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/cPanel-Server-Management-Serivce.png" /></a></p>
<h1 style="font-size: 3.5em; color: #2d70ca;">Server Management</h1>
<p><span class="dropcap"> S </span>imply put, <strong>server management</strong> is the maintenance and management of web server to keep it running in top condition. Today IT server management is not an option, it’s an essential requirement. Poorly managed or unmanaged servers usually end up getting hacked, important data loss and downtime. It will result in business loss due to downtime, harm your reputation and it will also drag your existing customer away to your competitors,  In short it’s going to make your life a living hell. While properly managed server will make your life easier and you can concentrate on managing your sales and marketing to grow your web hosting and other business.  Today lots of hosting companies provides VPS, cloud and dedicated servers but they don&#8217;t  provide <strong>server management services</strong> and solutions.  Hiring local dedicated <strong>24&#215;7 Server Management</strong> Staff to manage your servers will cost you both time and money. First of all you will have to train them about Windows and Linux Server management, Also you will have to keep them updated with latest technology in managing servers. That&#8217;s why most of the companies outsource their <strong>server management</strong> tasks to a good server management company, as outsourcing provides excellent quality support at cheap prices.  Choosing the <strong>best 24&#215;7 server management company</strong> is not an easy task. So <a href="/why-choose-servertechsupport">why choose  ServerTechSupport </a> for you <strong>server management</strong> tasks. The same stands if you have a web hosting business, hiring outsourced staff for your web hosting technical support is the best option. Because the outsourced support are fully whitelabled. Your customers are never going to know that you have outsourced your web hosting support team to a server management company.</p>
<div style="clear: both; padding: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;"></div>
<div class="half">
<h2 id="server-management-company"><a href="#server-management-company">Server Management Company</a></h2>
<hr />
<p>Server Tech Support is one of the India&#8217;s leading <strong>server management company</strong>.  ServerTechSupport offers different levels of cost effective <strong>outsourced server management</strong> and web hosting support services for <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linux">Linux</a> and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windows_Server">Windows</a> Servers. We will manage and monitor your server 24x7x365. Our services include <strong>24/7 server management services</strong>, technical support, server security with server monitoring . Whether you are a company or an individual owning vps, dedicated and cloud servers with Windows or Linux operating system, We are going to manage your server.</p>
<p>Also not everybody needs monthly server management, sometimes they just need one time fix for their issues on Linux or Windows servers. That&#8217;s why we also have hourly server management plan under which we do one time tasks. We also provide application server management for servers running open source or custom softwares and applications.</p>
<p>If you are looking for one the <strong>best server management companies</strong> then you have come to the right place.</div><div class="half last">
<h2>24&#215;7 Server Management Service</h2>
<hr />
<p>Your servers are the heart of your IT Infrastructure. Any downtime means a massive loss in productivity for your end-users. That&#8217;s why installing, securing, maintaining and managing your vital business infrastructure is critical to your business success. Tired of your current <strong>24&#215;7 Server Management</strong> provider? Losing your clients due to frequent Server Down Times? how do you go about choosing a <strong>24&#215;7 server management company</strong> that is trustworthy and reliable? AsThere are lots of companies that offer 24&#215;7 Server management services. Click <a href="/why-choose-servertechsupport">here</a> to see why you should choose ServerTechSupport for your Server Management. It&#8217;s time to sleep well &amp; spend more time on your business. <strong>ServerTechSupport&#8217;s</strong> server management plans ensure high levels of server reliability and uptime. ServerTechSupport team of system administrators are available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year to help you. We support both <a href="http://www.linux.org/">Linux</a> and <a href="http://windows.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/home">Windows</a> Servers. This will include <strong>24/7 server management</strong>, server monitoring, unlimited hours of system administration tasks, <a href="/server-security-service">server security hardening</a>, security auditing and performance tuning. All you need to do is submit a ticket with our 24/7 helpdesk system.</div><div class="clearf"></div></p>
<hr />
<h3>24&#215;7 Server Management for Windows and Linux Servers</h3>
<p>We have designed custom plans depending on the control panel on the server. So that it will be easier for you to choose the server management plan the best suites your need. It also covers Linux servers with control panel. Whether you are an individual, small business, or a Web hosting firm, we&#8217;ll fully manage and administer your servers.We realize the need for your servers to be running 100% of the time as well as being updated with the most current software. It is our job to manage your servers 24x7x365. Managing servers can be a difficult and time consuming task, even for the most experienced technician. In addition, not everyone is capable of fixing and monitoring their servers all hours of the day. We’re here to take that responsibility off your shoulders.</p>
