<p>ServerTechSupport is global leader in providing outsourced <strong>server support services</strong>. We are aware that each business is unique and it has it&#8217;s own set of IT and server support requirement. That&#8217;s why we also provide custom tailored server support services to meet the individual need of the customers at affordable rates apart from our regular <strong>server support</strong> plans. Our mission to provide high quality Windows &amp; Linux server management &amp; server support for CentOS, RedHat, Ubuntu, Debian and Windows 2003/2008/2012 servers.</p>
<p>Our team of Microsoft &amp; RedHat Certified IT support professionals have come together with a sole aim of providing unparalleled expert <strong>server support</strong> and management services to our clients. We are committed to provide expert server support services and guidance to our customers to enable their business growth extraordinarily.</p>
<p>Offering <strong>server support services</strong> and server management solutions at affordable prices is our unique selling point and that is what makes us different and helps us gain edge over competition.</div>
<div class="tabbed" id="tab-19271"><h4 class="tab_title">Outsourced Web Hosting Technical Support</h4>
<p><strong>ServerTechSupport</strong> offers excellent quality and cost effective <strong>outsourced web technical hosting support</strong>, IT support services for ISP&#8217;s , data centers and web hosting companies round the clock &#8211; 24x7x365. Our specialization spans over outsourced web technical hosting support, software support, sales support, remote server management and server monitoring service.</p>
<p>We support all major operating system like CentOS, RHEL, Debian, FreeBSD, Fedora, Ubuntu, Windows 2003/2008 with Control Panel like cPanel, Plesk, DirectAdmin, Kloxxo, Webmin, SolusVM, Virtuozzo, HyperVM or servers with no control panel. We also support the following virtualization &#8211; OpenVZ, Virtuozzo, Xen, KVM and VMWare (ESX, ESXi).</p>
<p><strong>Web hosting technical support</strong> provided by ServerTechSupport is completely transparent. It means your client will never know that their support queries are responded by somebody else other than you.<br />
If you are looking for a quality 24&#215;7 hosting support company then ServerTechSupport is the best choice for you.</div>
